creator: e-learning
descriptionHtml:
German is one of the major languages of the world. It is the most spoken native language within the European Union. German is also widely taught as a foreign language, especially in continental Europe, where it is the third most taught foreign language, and the United States.

This handy app will make your German learning easier and more effective. With thousands of beautifully illustrated words and native pronunciations, you won't get bored while learning the German language.

What will you learn in our "Learn German Language" app?

+ Learn German alphabet: you can learn German letters with alphabet games.
+ Topics: Colors, Animals, Fruits, Food, Shapes, Insects, Clothes, Nature, Clothes, Vehicle, Appliances, etc.
+ Listening Game: choose the right picture by listening the sound.
+ Picture Pickup: with the word, pick the right picture.
+ Picture Match: fun game to improve your German vocabulary.
+ Word Game: improve spelling ability by building the word from single letters.
+ 30+ languages supported.

Let's learn German now.
descriptionShort: Learn to speak German for beginners. Learn German through word games.
